column5: Ok guys and Gals if you have been sitting around waiting to get out from Port Maitland to chase Walleye this is the week calling for NORTH winds all week and in the 5 to 10k max Yahoo....Get out the Walleye are there

Thanx for the update Steve....  Nice eyes ya got there...WTG.... Can't wait, I only have a 16' so the calm Northerly breeze will be a blessing... What are they hitting? Oh and are they still on the bottm, or have they suspended?  Willy
Great pics Steve. That last pic shows a walleye with a large gash (in your left hand). Any idea what might have caused that?
Nice results! What happened to the second walleye in the picture, someone get hungry on the boat?
Not to sure on the gash might have been the knife in the cooler

Great going steve, I was out there last week with ya,  It was funny, I was out there before you came out, then I see you coming and it was like a duck with ducklings.. all the boats lineing up behind you  trolling along  Winds in the right direction and I am busy
Lex you fishing the SLA tourney Sun.?
Its going to be a good tourney ..one day im on big fish the next small
